      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis remains rigid with zero subframe issues, and the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides precise damping across all modes. Meticulously maintained with comprehensive service history including preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or trim degradation. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning collector.",
